# OS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets — never commit
**/.env

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/venv/

# Local data & artifacts (DB, audio, transcripts, reports, backups)
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal
**/data/audio/
**/data/transcripts/
**/data/coaching-reports/
**/data/backups/

# Runtime PID files
**/*.pid

# Personal config — kept local-only; see the *.example templates in config/
**/config/profile.md
**/config/companies.yaml

# Logs & models (large / machine-local)
**/logs/
**/models/

# Local edit-backup snapshots (git history supersedes these)
**/*.bak
**/*.bak-*

# Frontend (future)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
